Description: Handle of pottery transport amphora.. Rectangular stamp
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.31,6. Seems not to be identical with either British Museum 2011,5002.58 or 1925,0119.166. Name, Agoranax.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.1182)
